# Group Campaigns/Ratings
The Rating of a Campaign can be accessed and updated here.

## Rating [/campaigns/:id/rating/?include=includes]
Get the Rating that the Campaign is using 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Campaign to perform action with. Has example value.

