## Rating [/campaigns/:id/rating/:subid/?include=includes]
Get the Rating that the campaign is using by ID 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Campaign to perform action with. Has example value.
    + subid (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Rating to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Rating by ID [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                data: {
                  modified_by: null
                  name: "PG"
                  minimum_age: 10
